title: Have not received my gift get yet
body: okay this is whats up, I have not received my gift yet or my mystery gift or any Rp, I have kayle and the skin so. But when am I gonna get the mystery gift or the Rp, riot help me I want my free stuff ;){{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}}

replies.body: We're happy to provide you with the free stuff, but there are a lot of eligible accounts so it's going to take some time to give it all out.  Per our curren[t support ticker](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-), you may not get everything all at once.  Hang tight until this is all done!
i suppose patience is key to immortality :P
